review: Doctor is good she explained everything in a way that I could understand. I am looking forward to my next appointment where she would probably be doing an internal observation and examination and tell me exactly what I should be doing or following in terms of staying healthy and happy.

Consultation experience was good, I didn't have any negative feedback, everything was well and she understood everything and she listened to all my problems. I am satisfied with the doctor and doctor treatment. There was not much waiting time for the doctor. I would like to recommend this doctor to others. When it comes to improvement, Everything is good and the staff was supportive.

Would never recommend going here. I had an appointment for 1.30 pm and reached on time. The person on the reception said, dr isn't available for 2 hours and we don't take appointments from practo. on insisting, he called the doctor and asked to wait for 30mnts. I waited for more than 2 hours and doctor wasn't still there. on asking, he said I can't do anything. I had to leave without seeing d doctor after wasting almost 3 hours waiting for her. Please remove the listing from practo or improve your service instead of wasting people's time.
We have not consulted the doctor as we have booked the appointment at 12:30 waited till now and some doctor gave scanning for that also we need to wait for 1:30 mins

Doctor behaviour was good and listened to our problem properly. There was not much waiting time to consult the doctor and everything was good. I would like to give a rating of 4/5 and I'm satisfied with the doctor's treatment.
